Name: Cosmodome
About the game: Welcome to the Cosmodome, the greatest intergalactic sport in this side of the universe! Cosmodome is a: wrestling inspired, Intergalactic, ship combat game where the audience decides who wins or loses. Bash, blast and crash your way to victory with characters such as your average human, Dave , all the way to the jacked up and boneless Big Schlug . Local 4 player carnage Simple twin-stick + bumper control! 4 different playable characters with their own personality, stats, and weapons to own the dome. Approval based system where the winner is decided on the audience reaction!
